column5: Rick..you jinxed it by bragging about it in the stats thread...LOL.  I had that 'exceeded bandwidth' error for the past little while.
I don't care what my wife thinks. I didn't nothin' to nothin'!
Someone forgot to reset our bandwidth allotment when we moved over to the new private server...I will be sending emails tomorrow to certain people in Virginia.
You want I should pay someone a visit?
I say we send plummas, the goat, a broomstick and the goat!!   Apparently the last threat wasn't taken very seriously.
DDDDDDDDon't dddo tttttthat aaaggggain gggguys.  Really had me wondering what I was going to do for the next few evenings.
you forget to knock on wood Rick when you typed this
Don't forget to send the rooster also!!
I don't think you're ever over looked Roy, figuratively speaking of course.
